Packages 
Package Description
msp.simulator
MSP Numerical Simulator - Main package.
msp.simulator.dynamic
Dynamic Engine of the Simulation.
msp.simulator.dynamic.forces
This package implements all of the linear interaction between the environment and the satellite.
msp.simulator.dynamic.guidance
Gather all of the guidance services and processing method, i.e. the attitude law of the satellite over time.
msp.simulator.dynamic.propagation
This package gather all of the objects responsible for processing a controlled propagation of all of the satellite defined states through the environment.
msp.simulator.dynamic.test
Gather the test cases of the dynamic engine.
msp.simulator.dynamic.torques
Provide all of the models and tools to efficiently handle the contribution of any torque on the satellite over the time.
msp.simulator.environment
The package Environment is responsible to build and maintain all of the necessary modules of the simulation related to the space environment.
msp.simulator.environment.atmosphere
The package Atmosphere gathers the different classes of the simulator responsible for building any instance of the atmosphere of a planet.
msp.simulator.environment.geomagneticField
This package provides tools to access and maintain the GeoMagnetic Field object in the simulation.
msp.simulator.environment.gravitationalPotential
Gather the models of gravitational potential of the space environment.
msp.simulator.environment.orbit
The package Orbit gathers the different classes of the simulator responsible for building any instance of the orbit around a planet.
msp.simulator.environment.solarSystem
The package Solar System gathers the different classes of the simulator responsible for building the several instance of the Celestial Bodies of the Solar System.
msp.simulator.satellite
The Satellite package represents the overall satellite object in the simulation.
msp.simulator.satellite.actuators
Gather all of the models of actuators of the satellite.
msp.simulator.satellite.assembly
The assembly of the satellite is responsible to set up and maintain all of the components and services related to the satellite body, states, etc.
msp.simulator.satellite.sensors
This package gathers all of the sensor modules of the satellite.
msp.simulator.user
This package gathers all of the user-related method to performs an appropriate simulation.
msp.simulator.utils
This package contains any kind of tools and components relevant for the good processing of the numerical simulator.
msp.simulator.utils.architecture
Gather the tools and methods for a formal simulator architecture.
msp.simulator.utils.logs
This package provides tools and methods to handle to logging services.
msp.simulator.utils.logs.ephemeris
This package is responsible to provide a set of tools and method to create the ephemerides all along the simulation processing, especially including the propagation of the dynamic parameters.
